.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
deploy/iac/terraform.tfvars
/deploy/compose/data
/data
# Python bytecode (bench/ tooling + the scale-test harness)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
# Rendered per-workload k8s manifests (task-214) — regenerate with `harness.py render <workload>`
/bench/scale/.render/
.claude/
